{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing "},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(described below)."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The first week of the year is week 1.  This is the week that contains","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the first Thursday of the year.  Equivalently, this is the first week"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"that has more than 4 of its days falling within the calendar year.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The value 0 is never returned by this function.  Days contained","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"within a year but occurring before the first ISO 8601 week of that"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"year are considered as being contained in the last week of the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"previous year.  Similarly, the final days of a calendar year may be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"considered as being part of the first ISO 8601 week of the next year"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"if 4 or more days of that week are contained within the new year."}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol\/weekofyear"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"extendedModule":"GLib","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:4GLib16DateTimeProtocolPAAE10weekOfYearSivp","modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"title":"weekOfYear","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol\/weekOfYear","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeProtocol/weekOfYear":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing "},{"code":"datetime","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual results"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(described below)."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol\/weekOfYear","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol\/weekofyear","title":"weekOfYear","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/DateTimeProtocol":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DateTimeProtocol","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDateTime"},{"text":" is a structure that combines a Gregorian date and time","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"into a single structure."}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DateTimeProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"DateTimeProtocol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DateTimeProtocol","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/datetimeprotocol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"url":"\/documentation\/glib","kind":"symbol","title":"GLib","abstract":[],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","role":"collection"}}}